name: Who is Dealer
description:
Who is Dealer is a jam game made for DevLeague Season 1.

Theme: Unfinished Business.

Lore?

Demon wanted you to go to hell, but you said,

" First let me complete the Unfinished Business, Bro"

Is game playable?

*  No, you can move around the map, but there is no win or end to this.

How to play?

* Use WASD keys to move around.

* Your main objective is to find the dealer.

Why not completed?

* I had to go for a event so this is what I was able to make in 3 hours. :)
